    Ahava is the act of love.
    Strong's Exhaustive Dictionary
  </p>
    <p>Doulas are trained professionals who provide loving, non judgemental, physical, emotional and informational support so birthing families can feel confident and ready to start their journey into parenthood. A doula can support you to gather information and make choices that feel good for your family throughout pregnancy, birth and postpartum.</p>
